{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "14-14", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "高空拒阻行動", "storyInfo": "特蕾西婭控制的飛空艇似乎準備撞向“阿喃那”。W和博士眾人緊急制定了跳幫登上飛空艇，阻止特蕾西婭和“阿喃那”的計畫。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g1_shard_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "碎片大廈之中，粉白短髮的薩卡茲再度孤身一人。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這裡還遠算不上是戰場前沿，但戰爭的聲音還是毫無阻礙地穿過山谷，穿過城牆，穿過結晶的風暴與血的羅網，傳進了他的耳中。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "源石火炮傾瀉著死亡之雨，軍團術師們正喃喃吟唱，戰車的履帶軋過一片又一片結晶潮，刀劍崩出豁口，最終落進污泥之中。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這樣的聲音，他已經聽了數百年，從未改變。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只不過這次，是他把這些帶來了曾經的加害者們的家園。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏薩斯的皇帝拒絕接見我們的使者，他們依然將卡茲戴爾視作一個獨立的敵方政權。", "name": "終端裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "派往薩爾貢的使者還沒有回信，萊塔尼亞的那位選帝侯表達了積極交流的意願……", "name": "終端裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大公爵們在戰場上那道金光出現之後，進攻意圖十分明顯。我們的外圍陣線正在收縮……", "name": "終端裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終端裡的聲音仍在忠實地為這場戰爭的主導者彙報著每一條戰線的最新動向。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭的天平正微微搖晃，不願屈服的人們將自己化作砝碼，一次次渴望改變它傾斜的方向。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論在什麼時候，特雷西斯的背脊都永遠筆挺，他早已不會讓自己輕易感覺到疲憊。"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但一切積累的過往都不會輕易消逝，無論是被拯救的，還是被殺死的。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，他也從來不曾忘記肩膀上的重量，尤其是在它們越來越難以承擔的當下。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下，前線傳來消息……維多利亞的國劍已啟動，他們遏制了“阿喃那”的攻勢。我們的戰況吃緊。", "name": "王庭軍親衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一方面，曼弗雷德將軍，也未能奪回“生命脊椎”。", "name": "王庭軍親衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "骸骨現在被誰掌控，最後的目擊位置在哪裡？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一支傭兵小隊。赦罪師那邊通報，上面應該還有那個名叫“羅德島”的組織的核心成員。", "name": "王庭軍親衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“羅德島”……那個人，想必也在吧。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#2$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i10_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍，我們無法確定“生命脊椎”的下一步動向。它對飛空艇和碎片大廈都是威脅。", "name": "王庭軍親衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無妨，相信特蕾西婭。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果他們敢靠近碎片大廈……", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#3$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的劍會賜予那個人我承諾過的審判。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#2$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆的天空早已被紅色浸染，永不彌散的陰雲已不復存在，在無數枝蔓的托舉下，巨大的晶體如同剛剛結出的果實。"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切已經準備就緒。"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但此時，唯有此時，他卻不想去思考有關未來的一切。"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "飛空艇漫長的盤旋與試探已經接近尾聲，巫術的巨構又一次掠過碎片大廈的上空。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他知道，這是最後一次了。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g9_airshipdockcorridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "航行的飛空艇之中，粉白長髮的薩卡茲獨自佇立在走廊裡。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的視線終於從碎片大廈移開，她已不會再看見那個人的身影。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭的目光投向飛空艇的陰影中，投向這片她已經看過無數次的大地。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "心碎和絕望仍在蔓延。這片大地如今的模樣，與當年她離開卡茲戴爾的時候……有了分別嗎？"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "低沉的聲音在她身邊迴盪，那是這艘船的主人。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭，我能感知到——那位“魔王”，仍在追逐我們。", "name": "船艙中的影子"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他們都不是輕言放棄的人。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#2$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呵。", "name": "船艙中的影子"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死魂靈不再言語，飛空艇開始了最後的提速。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“原點”已經近在眼前。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虛幻的浪潮卻驟然湧來，時間與空間的亂流在飛空艇周身盤旋。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們來了——", "name": "船艙中的影子"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這點星火，一定會為我們燃盡腐朽。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#2$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，就看看他們能走多遠吧。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g1_giantmonstercockpit", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_smog", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這骨頭架子真是這麼開的嗎？！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#5$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷真的說服了這具骨頭老老實實幫我們？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#6$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這你得問他。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他現在連一句完整的話都說不出來，我問他？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#6$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就相信他。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嘖。他最好沒搞錯什麼步驟。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，現在這個骨頭架子也回到我們手裡了，是不是該去執行最初的計劃了？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用這個塞滿炸彈的大傢伙，把碎片大廈和特雷西斯炸上天。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "有更重要的問題擺在我們面前。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line148"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "“阿喃那”現在的狀態怎麼樣了？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line150"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_aircraftfall"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從舷窗裡可以看到，風暴雖然已經停息，但天空還是一片令人不安的赤紅。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“阿喃那”，像是天空的創口，高懸在碎片大廈的正上空。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "飛空艇正徑直飛向本不該存在於世的古老遺跡，接近這片大地最深奧的秘密。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "飛空艇，正在向“阿喃那”飛去。;特雷西斯始終沒有在戰場上動用它。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line160", "option2": "line160"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那只有一種解釋。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起被當作武器，它還有更重要的使命。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "他難道是想讓飛空艇撞向那塊“源石”？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line168"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "“阿喃那”的內部有什麼？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line170"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，兜帽人，她這意思是在殺死特雷西斯之前，需要先解決飛空艇。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯吧，老女人？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們就先把飛空艇打下來再說。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是誰在駕駛飛空艇？;特雷西斯還會相信誰？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line183", "option2": "line183"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#15$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能感受得到……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她……特蕾西婭小姐在那裡，是嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是的。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們去追擊飛空艇，接下來的戰鬥，毫無疑問會直面她。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要做好——", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想說，我們要做好殺了她的準備？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#13$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果……這是必須的。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真了不起。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#12$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為你和殿下關係還不錯呢。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#12$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希，你是不是永遠都在做這樣的權衡？文明啦，大地啦——為了這些東西，你可以殺掉任何人。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕……她是特蕾西婭。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我和你不一樣，凱爾希。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#6$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會從眾魂中救出殿下，我會結束這一切。如果你們不想做，那就我來做。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#6$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等著瞧吧……等著瞧吧。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#6$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會再有一次背叛了。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我有理由相信，此時此地，你是最能保持理智的人。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來的所有作戰指揮，希望可以交給你。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "好。;交給我吧。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line223", "option2": "line223"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別光說好聽的，我們到底要怎麼拿下飛空艇？這骨頭架子上的武器怎麼看都不夠多。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "不是“拿下”，是“運走”。;用“生命脊椎”的力量傳送飛空艇。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line229", "option2": "line229"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣可以？那個飛空艇看起來可是和骨頭架子差不多大。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#5$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的戰術變得很激進啊。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "沒有追求穩妥的餘裕了。;這是最後的機會。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line237", "option2": "line237"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確是唯一的辦法，且值得一試。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會盡力為骸骨提供庇護，以應對飛空艇的炮火。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能讓骸骨接觸到飛空艇，我們就有勝機。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信博士，我也可以協助Logos先生。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然大家都同意這個計劃，W……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "讓“生命脊椎”漂流到飛空艇上方。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line249"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈……搞得好像我怕了一樣。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老骨頭，醒醒，我們又要出發了！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都抓好了！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幻境消散，漣漪歸於平靜。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只一瞬間，他們的身下，已是——"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energycannon"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "