tent": "能量漸漸消散，主炮的射擊終於結束。"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "飛空艇中的巫術陣列放大了死魂靈術法的力量。我們無法抵禦第二次主炮的轟擊。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抓緊時間，靠近飛空艇。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4133_logos_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無數的巫術無人機已經升空，身著染血長袍的巫靈們騰空而起。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們皆已向骸骨所在的位置奔襲而來。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些人的反應真是夠快的！還真忍心啊……這骨頭架子不是他們的寶貝嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特雷西斯打算讓我們跟骨頭架子一起直接蒸發在這裡？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W小姐，還差一點，這個距離“生命脊椎”沒有辦法與飛空艇連接！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，飛空艇的火力有點猛，我們是沒辦法安穩靠近了！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#9$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，你們想來點刺激的嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1035_wisdel_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只能——這樣！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": 